1/3

@BleepinComputer 1.  Yes it is a terrible breach, and it is 5.4 million accounts.

3. Credentials are not included... 

SOOOOOO what should be aware of?

2/3

Verify all emails from any sender & don't click links go direct to your account

Do not share your credentials with any unverified person.

Do not jump on the FUD train and join in trying to paint this as more than what it is.
